<subSubSection id="48D355CA8FF8FE7648F757B4FEABFEEC" pageId="438" pageNumber="439" type="discussion">
<paragraph id="007606418FF8FE7648F757B4FEABFEEC" blockId="438.[151,1436,151,284]" pageId="438" pageNumber="439">
<emphasis id="32BDDA538FF8FE7648F757B4FE9EFF40" bold="true" box="[199,315,152,176]" pageId="438" pageNumber="439">Remarks.</emphasis>
The 
<typeStatus id="DF72B8E38FF8FE76494A57B4FE0FFF40" box="[378,426,152,176]" pageId="438" pageNumber="439">type</typeStatus>
of this species has been deposited in the Pusa Imperial College collection (now 
<collectionCode id="66D89E848FF8FE764D6257BBFA34FF5F" box="[1362,1425,151,175]" country="India" httpUri="http://biocol.org/urn:lsid:biocol.org:col:13272" lsid="urn:lsid:biocol.org:col:13272" name="Indian Agricultural Research Institute" pageId="438" pageNumber="439">IARI</collectionCode>
). However, now it is apparently lost. Probably this species belongs to 
<taxonomicName id="C7C97DC28FF8FE764B9B5791FBA0FF24" authorityName="Latreille" authorityYear="1804" box="[939,1029,189,212]" class="Insecta" family="Dryinidae" genus="Dryinus" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Hymenoptera" pageId="438" pageNumber="439" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">
<emphasis id="32BDDA538FF8FE764B9B5791FBA0FF24" box="[939,1029,189,212]" italics="true" pageId="438" pageNumber="439">Dryinus</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
(
<taxonomicName id="C7C97DC28FF8FE764C285790FB01FF24" authorityName="R. Perkins" authorityYear="1905" box="[1048,1188,188,212]" class="Insecta" family="Dryinidae" genus="Paradryinus" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Hymenoptera" pageId="438" pageNumber="439" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">
<emphasis id="32BDDA538FF8FE764C285790FB01FF24" box="[1048,1188,188,212]" italics="true" pageId="438" pageNumber="439">Paradryinus</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
is junior synonym of 
<taxonomicName id="C7C97DC28FF8FE7648A757CCFF54FF07" authorityName="Latreille" authorityYear="1804" box="[151,241,224,247]" class="Insecta" family="Dryinidae" genus="Dryinus" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Hymenoptera" pageId="438" pageNumber="439" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">
<emphasis id="32BDDA538FF8FE7648A757CCFF54FF07" box="[151,241,224,247]" italics="true" pageId="438" pageNumber="439">Dryinus</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
), but the original description is insufficient to make possible its inclusion in the keys to the 
<collectingRegion id="C20DC8A38FF8FE764D7057F3FA39FF07" box="[1344,1436,223,247]" country="Democratic Republic of the Congo" name="Orientale" pageId="438" pageNumber="439">Oriental</collectingRegion>
<taxonomicName id="C7C97DC28FF8FE7648A75628FEAEFEEC" authorityName="Haliday" authorityYear="1833" box="[151,267,260,284]" class="Insecta" family="Dryinidae" kingdom="Animalia" order="Hymenoptera" pageId="438" pageNumber="439" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="family">Dryinidae</taxonomicName>
.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
